=Datamung

==Introduction

Datamung is a Java open source, web based,
[http://aws.amazon.com/swf|AWS&nbsp;Simple&nbsp;Workflow]
driven solution that backs up AWS RDS MySQL database into S3 object by launching
EC2 instance and running mysqldump command. It makes it possible to replicate
RDS across regions, VPC, accounts or outside AWS network.

