</p>

Datamung is one of the ten winners of
[http://techblog.netflix.com/2013/11/netflix-open-source-software-cloud.html|2013&nbsp;Netflix&nbsp;Cloud&nbsp;Prize]
award. On Nov 14th 2013, during the
[http://youtu.be/Waq8Y6s1Cjs?t=13m17s|day&nbsp;2&nbsp;keynote&nbsp;session]
of AWS re:invent conference in Las Vegas, it was announced as the winner of
datastore integration category. Check out
[http://blog.cyclopsgroup.org/2013/11/datamung-won-netflix-cloud-prize-award.html|this&nbsp;blog]
for stories behind scene.

